Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:04.43,0:00:05.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人與人的邂逅充滿了神奇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:05.99,0:00:07.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各種刑案更是謎題重重
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:07.60,0:00:09.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能夠遇到你真的是太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:09.92,0:00:11.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次的事件是可疑的車輛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:11.65,0:00:12.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要小心交通事故喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:13.52,0:00:14.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唯一看透真相的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:15.02,0:00:15.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是一個外表看似小孩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:15.93,0:00:16.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,智慧卻過於常人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:16.91,0:00:18.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他的名字是 名偵探柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:40.35,0:01:43.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偵探團大追擊事件
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:50.66,0:01:52.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,步美 光彥 元太 他過去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:53.39,0:01:54.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們知道了 柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:55.02,0:01:56.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,交給我們沒問題啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:56.61,0:01:57.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們都已經準備好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:08.45,0:02:08.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看我的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:16.71,0:02:18.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放開我 快放我下去呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:18.97,0:02:20.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少年偵探團
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:20.78,0:02:21.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又成功了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:27.09,0:02:28.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管什麼案件我們都可以接受
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:29.17,0:02:29.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們一定會追查
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:30.27,0:02:31.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再把它解開
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:32.98,0:02:34.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們吹牛也吹得太誇張一點了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:35.50,0:02:38.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有事情就交給我們少年偵探團吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:55.59,0:02:57.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你們的招待
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:58.11,0:02:58.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:59.15,0:03:00.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然給我吃了這麼多的東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:01.09,0:03:03.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們幾個小鬼知不知道什麼叫客氣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:04.93,0:03:06.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這些小朋友這次立了大功
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:06.88,0:03:09.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你可要好好的請他們吃一頓 毛利老弟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:10.76,0:03:11.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要我請他們吃飯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:14.23,0:03:17.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個月的零用錢這下全都沒了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:18.51,0:03:19.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是你們還真厲害
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:20.15,0:03:22.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是犯案高達五十次的強盜耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:22.45,0:03:23.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他裝成寶石店的客人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:24.04,0:03:26.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是柯南最先發現那個人有點不太一樣的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:27.79,0:03:28.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那也是我偶然發現的啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:29.67,0:03:31.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以後會有更多人拜託我們辦案了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:32.46,0:03:33.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我們就可以開事務所了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:46.65,0:03:47.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有車過來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:50.34,0:03:50.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,步美
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:51.47,0:03:51.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:52.43,0:03:54.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新宿33な33－96
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:55.63,0:03:56.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它撞了人就跑啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:57.42,0:03:59.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小蘭 你們留在這個地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:59.49,0:04:01.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我這就去聯絡救護車和警方過來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:01.74,0:04:02.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡就拜託妳了 小蘭姐姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:06.77,0:04:08.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼都不用說了 柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:08.61,0:04:10.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這件事情絕對不能交給警察去辦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:11.27,0:04:13.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那好 你們兩個可要抓緊了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:24.05,0:04:24.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那輛車轉彎了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:25.27,0:04:26.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,速度再不快點的話會追不上的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:27.23,0:04:27.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我當然知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:33.83,0:04:34.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是歹徒的車子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:35.36,0:04:37.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還以為追不上呢 太幸運了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:51.09,0:04:52.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他又停下來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:52.62,0:04:54.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看一定是車子的引擎不太好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:55.56,0:04:56.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們的運氣實在太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:57.54,0:04:58.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每次轉彎的時候就停車
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:59.84,0:05:01.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,簡直像是故意在等我們追上一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:05.31,0:05:05.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他逃掉了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:06.94,0:05:07.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在幹什麼 柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:08.13,0:05:09.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點 讓速度再快一點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:22.95,0:05:24.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那輛車子怎麼不見啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:24.94,0:05:26.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次真的讓他逃掉了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:26.76,0:05:27.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快去找
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:31.88,0:05:33.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他會不會是躲到這個地方來了呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:35.12,0:05:36.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會吧 這裡沒有能躲的地方呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:37.70,0:05:39.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且這個工廠好像也沒有上班
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:40.69,0:05:41.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們繞到後面去看看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:46.74,0:05:47.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這條路太爛了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:48.18,0:05:49.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼都沒有鋪柏油呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:55.01,0:05:56.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡是樓梯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:56.85,0:05:57.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼說來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:58.62,0:05:59.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒看見
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:00.06,0:06:01.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個地方有一家賣香煙的小店
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:01.99,0:06:02.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們去問問看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:07.36,0:06:09.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,婆婆 剛才有沒有一輛紅色的車子經過呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:10.34,0:06:11.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:11.86,0:06:14.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我記得好像有兩三輛車子經過吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:14.90,0:06:15.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是輛兩門的車子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:16.01,0:06:17.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是一輛跑車
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:17.73,0:06:19.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我根本搞不清是車子的樣子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:24.87,0:06:27.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來是你 你最近好不好呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:29.34,0:06:30.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們到這裡來花了三分鐘了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:31.51,0:06:32.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看他一定是跑掉了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:33.45,0:06:33.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:36.31,0:06:37.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們快看那個地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:37.97,0:06:38.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那輛紅色的車子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:38.82,0:06:39.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定是他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:40.57,0:06:41.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它又不能動了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:41.94,0:06:42.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們運氣真好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:43.78,0:06:44.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:44.43,0:06:45.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這跟以前不一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:46.25,0:06:48.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才那裡明明沒有車子的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:48.87,0:06:49.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它是倒車回來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:50.49,0:06:51.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這又是為什麼呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:54.97,0:06:56.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次一定要把他逮到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:56.82,0:06:57.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次他逃不掉了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:09.16,0:07:10.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好 就差一點點了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:11.72,0:07:12.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:20.66,0:07:22.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:22.82,0:07:23.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,派出所
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:27.89,0:07:28.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,警察先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:28.94,0:07:29.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點把我抓起來吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:30.41,0:07:31.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我剛才撞到人後逃走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:32.76,0:07:34.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他自首了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:38.33,0:07:41.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個人雖然在撞到步美之後立刻把車子開走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:42.15,0:07:45.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是他好像覺得有罪惡感 所以就去自首了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:45.80,0:07:47.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 太掃興了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:47.87,0:07:50.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們本來還想多發揮一下少年偵探團的威力的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:51.80,0:07:52.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柯南你怎麼了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:54.55,0:07:55.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:55.54,0:07:57.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了 步美的傷有沒有怎麼樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:58.27,0:08:00.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼 還好只是受到一點擦傷而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:00.96,0:08:02.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,醫生說不用住院也沒有關係
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:03.95,0:08:05.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天就可以直接回家了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:05.76,0:08:06.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:07.47,0:08:08.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一點也不好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:09.10,0:08:11.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柯南好不容易幫我們少年偵探團做的徽章
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:12.52,0:08:13.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都被我弄掉了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:14.68,0:08:16.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那一定是被車撞的時候弄掉的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:17.43,0:08:18.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也問過那些警察叔叔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:19.08,0:08:19.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們都沒有看到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:20.62,0:08:21.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳不用擔心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:21.81,0:08:23.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿笠博士還可以幫妳再做一個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:24.45,0:08:24.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:25.46,0:08:25.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:26.57,0:08:28.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我最喜歡柯南了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:29.54,0:08:30.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你很奸詐哦 柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:31.30,0:08:33.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就會耍這些小聰明 太奸詐了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:34.03,0:08:35.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎喲喂呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:37.16,0:08:37.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們幾個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:38.16,0:08:40.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點跟我到四號街那裡的工廠去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:41.39,0:08:42.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,警部正在那裡等著呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:43.36,0:08:46.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,四號街的工廠? 我們剛才還經過那個地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:46.85,0:08:48.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底怎麼了 叔叔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:48.80,0:08:51.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽說那個工廠發現有人死在那裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:51.92,0:08:52.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,據說是個殺人案件
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:00.30,0:09:02.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽著 你們幾個就待在這裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:04.69,0:09:05.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,警部
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:06.42,0:09:07.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你終於來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:07.69,0:09:08.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我就直說了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:08.97,0:09:09.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,情況是這樣的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:11.08,0:09:12.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這名被害者是這個工廠的社長
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:13.44,0:09:14.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,石倉久志先生 今年五十歲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:16.03,0:09:17.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是謀財害命嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:19.86,0:09:23.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們現在的確是從強盜殺人的路線來進行調查的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:24.66,0:09:26.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天這家工廠雖然沒有上班
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:27.20,0:09:30.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是石倉先生據說是為了確認成品才到工廠來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:31.08,0:09:34.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他的嘴巴和手腕上面都有膠帶的痕跡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:35.65,0:09:37.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼說來 他曾經被人綁起來過
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:38.14,0:09:40.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過兇手為什麼又特意把膠帶給撕掉了呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:41.71,0:09:42.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個兇手…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:44.61,0:09:46.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犯罪現場不是讓你隨便亂跑的地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:46.48,0:09:47.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:51.57,0:09:54.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,後門這裡一出來就是這個賣香煙婆婆的攤位了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:57.18,0:09:58.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,詳細的資料必須等待解剖才會知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:59.75,0:10:02.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過估計死者的死亡時間應該是在一個小時以前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:03.75,0:10:06.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一個小時以前我們正好經過這個地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:07.21,0:10:07.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,錯不了的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:08.67,0:10:09.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然是這樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:10.00,0:10:12.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個時候你們有沒有看到什麼可疑的人物嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:13.02,0:10:14.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真要說起來的話 那個時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:15.69,0:10:18.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們一心在追那個開車撞人的人 所以沒注意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:19.41,0:10:20.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他就在這裡呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:21.34,0:10:24.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你自己看嘛 就是站在後排中間的那個人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:27.23,0:10:28.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是撞了步美之後開車就跑的歹徒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:29.76,0:10:31.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說什麼 是真的嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:31.96,0:10:32.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會有錯的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:33.53,0:10:35.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個殺人犯會不會是他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:36.15,0:10:38.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會吧 這是巧合啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:39.08,0:10:39.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是當然啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:40.39,0:10:41.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他開車撞人逃跑的途中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:42.19,0:10:43.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼可能會到這裡搶錢殺人嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:47.11,0:10:48.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我被那幾個小朋友追著跑的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:49.66,0:10:52.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的確是在那個工廠後門一點的轉彎角突然熄火停下來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:53.83,0:10:54.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:54.82,0:10:57.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我根本沒有把車子停在工廠後門的地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:58.68,0:10:59.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,更不可能殺人了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:01.42,0:11:02.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這只是巧合而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:03.56,0:11:05.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個傢伙以前還在那家工廠裡工作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:06.51,0:11:09.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上個月因為行為不檢的關係被公司解雇了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:10.08,0:11:11.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你該不會是說 警部
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:12.08,0:11:13.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那果然就是他了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:13.55,0:11:15.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這太不可能了 元太
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:16.11,0:11:16.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:17.07,0:11:17.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這還不簡單
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:17.95,0:11:20.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為那個時候我們幾個就在工廠的前面呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:20.64,0:11:21.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過 警部
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:22.31,0:11:24.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說不定這些孩子沒有看到的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:24.59,0:11:26.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他就從工廠的後門進入工廠了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:26.72,0:11:27.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:28.12,0:11:31.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個在工廠後門賣香煙的老太太她也跟我們證實了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:32.86,0:11:35.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我那個時候根本沒有看到哪裡有停車子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:36.35,0:11:38.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管工廠後門或是巷子裡面都沒有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:39.43,0:11:39.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管怎麼說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:40.40,0:11:43.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個香煙攤的位置正好對著工廠的入口
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:43.68,0:11:44.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以這個證詞應該是非常可靠
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:47.91,0:11:50.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼說來 這的確是個巧合了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:51.77,0:11:52.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:52.95,0:11:55.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這兩個案件的背後一定有什麼關係
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:56.35,0:11:57.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是我們沒有注意到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:58.32,0:11:59.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定有什麼關係才對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:03.23,0:12:05.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柯南 我們還要看什麼東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:05.84,0:12:09.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們快點去步美家看步美吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:10.07,0:12:11.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你們兩個就先去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:12.07,0:12:15.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行 既然我們都是少年偵探團的成員
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:15.56,0:12:17.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就必須要一起行動才行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:18.26,0:12:19.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這之前我想先喝果汁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:20.32,0:12:21.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我突然覺得口好渴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:22.20,0:12:23.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要喝果汁那裡就有賣的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:24.39,0:12:26.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看 就到那個香煙攤的前面買就行了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:32.60,0:12:34.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個小渡也真是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:34.52,0:12:36.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他以前一直很認真的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:37.84,0:12:38.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:39.97,0:12:40.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老婆婆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:41.35,0:12:42.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請問在工廠發生意外的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:43.08,0:12:44.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳有沒有接到打錯的電話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:46.35,0:12:46.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這麼一說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:47.00,0:12:49.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個時候的確有兩個打錯的電話呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:50.89,0:12:51.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想得果然沒錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:52.74,0:12:54.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我記得他是在岔路上面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:55.50,0:12:57.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝 老婆婆 再見
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:02.60,0:13:03.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎麼啦 柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:04.05,0:13:05.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,元太 你快背我上去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:06.20,0:13:06.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,背你上去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:10.40,0:13:11.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你發現了什麼東西嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:12.71,0:13:13.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然沒錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:15.06,0:13:16.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟我想的一模一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:19.20,0:13:19.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:21.25,0:13:22.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來是這樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:22.72,0:13:23.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來在那個地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:30.55,0:13:31.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:31.84,0:13:33.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帶撞人逃逸的宍戶健一過去嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:35.04,0:13:35.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了 毛利老弟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:36.71,0:13:38.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好 下一個是叔叔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:41.42,0:13:43.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毛利老弟嗎 我是目暮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:43.87,0:13:46.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能不能請你立刻趕到第四街的工廠這裡來一趟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:50.41,0:13:50.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家辛苦了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:55.18,0:13:56.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,警部 怎麼回事呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:57.12,0:13:58.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們等你很久了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:58.76,0:13:59.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們兩個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:00.24,0:14:02.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們兩個在這裡幹什麼呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:02.98,0:14:05.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目暮警部馬上會到這裡了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:05.46,0:14:07.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在他到這之前 你就坐在這裡等他吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:09.49,0:14:11.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們挺細心的嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:15.03,0:14:20.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最起碼也應該讓我喝一口以後再這樣對我吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:23.24,0:14:24.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柯南說得果然沒有錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:25.37,0:14:26.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他只要一到事件案發的現場
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:27.15,0:14:28.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馬上就會變成沉睡的小五郎了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:29.55,0:14:30.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們在空罐裡灌水的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:31.02,0:14:32.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他一定都知道了才對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:34.45,0:14:35.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柯南 你在哪裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:36.10,0:14:37.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下來該怎麼辦才好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:38.83,0:14:40.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我聽柯南跟我說過了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:41.22,0:14:42.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下面交給我就行了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:43.92,0:14:45.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪有這樣的呀 叔叔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:45.48,0:14:46.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們不用擔心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:47.02,0:14:49.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我早就準備好讓你們兩個出場的機會了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:50.23,0:14:51.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:51.30,0:14:52.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:55.49,0:14:57.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毛利老弟 我把人給帶來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:57.98,0:14:58.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底是怎麼回事呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:59.35,0:15:01.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想宍戶先生應該很清楚才對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:03.71,0:15:04.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這話怎麼說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:05.37,0:15:06.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你今天下午
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:06.86,0:15:09.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開車撞了一個少女後就開車逃跑了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:09.88,0:15:10.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:10.84,0:15:14.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就故意用這幾個孩子追得上你的速度開車引導他們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:14.75,0:15:16.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接著就來到了這裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:16.78,0:15:17.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為的就是把他們幾個帶到你所熟悉的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:17.80,0:15:18.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:18.48,0:15:22.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是懷有恨意的石倉先生的工廠來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:22.83,0:15:24.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不懂 你到底在說什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:26.26,0:15:28.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼說 你還是要我揭穿你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:29.87,0:15:31.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實殺害石倉先生的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:32.04,0:15:32.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宍戶先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:33.56,0:15:34.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:37.68,0:15:38.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在胡說什麼啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:39.42,0:15:42.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才關於石倉先生這件殺人案件
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:42.48,0:15:44.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們不是早就證明了他是清白的嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:45.22,0:15:45.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:46.32,0:15:49.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他在開車逃逸的途中是不可能同時殺人的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:49.85,0:15:51.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個理由的確可以減輕他的嫌疑沒錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:51.99,0:15:54.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要知道還有證人可以證明我的清白
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:55.68,0:15:57.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是這些追著我跑的小子們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:59.09,0:16:02.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是如果說你打從一開始就計畫讓這些孩子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:02.74,0:16:05.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是少年偵探團來為你做不在場證明的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:06.10,0:16:07.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,情況就不同了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:08.90,0:16:11.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說什麼 這話怎麼說呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:12.53,0:16:12.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:13.76,0:16:15.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他把步美撞倒 開車逃逸的事情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:16.20,0:16:20.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是為這宗殺人案件做的一個障眼法的話又怎麼說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:21.86,0:16:25.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會吧 這種事可以做到嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:25.91,0:16:26.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根據柯南的描述顯示
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:27.71,0:16:29.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個傢伙每次碰到彎道的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:29.59,0:16:31.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都會特意把車速儘量放慢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:31.86,0:16:33.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓柯南他們不會追不上他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:34.46,0:16:36.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果說他是想讓他們追上自己的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:36.95,0:16:38.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就可以解釋了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:38.69,0:16:40.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是因為我的車的情況的確是不太好呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:41.44,0:16:42.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他說得對 毛利老弟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:43.23,0:16:44.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們沒收那輛車以後發現
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:45.13,0:16:47.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算把火星塞換過以後 引擎還是沒有辦法啟動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:48.13,0:16:52.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼一點手腳就連外行人都可以做到 警部
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:54.57,0:16:56.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那好吧 就算真如你說的好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:57.36,0:16:58.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我也有不在場證明
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:59.66,0:17:01.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且是最完美的不在場證明
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:01.80,0:17:02.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的確
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:03.22,0:17:06.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除掉這些孩子沒有看到你的那三分鐘之外
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:08.85,0:17:10.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三分鐘根本不可能做什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:11.33,0:17:12.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,錯了 三分鐘足夠了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:13.44,0:17:14.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要進入工廠就行了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:16.52,0:17:17.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,簡直一派胡言
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:17.97,0:17:19.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我如果把車停在工廠後門的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:19.78,0:17:22.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,賣煙的老太太應該會看到我才對呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:23.05,0:17:24.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你倒是挺清楚的嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:25.28,0:17:27.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我以前也在這個工廠裡工作過
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:27.85,0:17:29.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會知道這是很自然的事情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:30.03,0:17:31.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼我想你一定也知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:32.75,0:17:34.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個香煙攤的電話號碼了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:36.64,0:17:39.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道你在胡說些什麼東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:40.08,0:17:42.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是沒有把車停在工廠的後門
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:42.92,0:17:45.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為你是用走的進入工廠的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:46.98,0:17:48.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼那輛車子會在哪裡呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:49.26,0:17:49.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,停到哪裡去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:50.54,0:17:50.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:53.00,0:17:54.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:54.71,0:17:56.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你剛剛跑到哪裡去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:57.35,0:17:58.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個不重要
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:58.60,0:18:00.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們兩個現在快帶警部
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:00.87,0:18:02.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到我剛才偷看的那個倉庫去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:03.46,0:18:04.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到那個倉庫去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:10.31,0:18:11.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這輛車子是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:13.07,0:18:14.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟那輛撞人逃逸的車子一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:15.03,0:18:16.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且就是這個車號
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:22.36,0:18:23.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宍戶先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:23.89,0:18:25.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼這裡會有一輛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:25.37,0:18:28.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟你撞人逃逸的時候開的一樣的車子呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:28.36,0:18:29.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:29.90,0:18:32.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想他是把車加以改裝了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:33.84,0:18:37.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然曾經在金屬烤漆工廠工作過的宍戶先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:37.80,0:18:39.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種事對你來說是輕而易舉的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:40.66,0:18:43.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想你大概是先到工廠的辦公室
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:43.73,0:18:45.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,利用麻醉藥或是什麼東西先讓石倉先生睡著以後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:46.44,0:18:48.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再用膠帶把石倉先生綁住留在工廠裡面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:49.69,0:18:51.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後開著改裝的車
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:51.56,0:18:53.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,進行一場撞人逃逸的意外
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:54.92,0:18:56.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接著又為了能讓那些孩子追得上你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:57.67,0:18:58.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一會兒突然把車停下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:59.47,0:19:00.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一會兒突然開車前進
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:01.40,0:19:02.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的目的就是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:03.01,0:19:05.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把這些孩子引到工廠的前面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:07.31,0:19:09.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後你就把車子藏到倉庫裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:10.72,0:19:11.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:11.76,0:19:14.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你用行動電話打給工廠後門賣香煙的老太太
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:14.90,0:19:18.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趁著老太太把身體轉向電話的時候通過香煙攤
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:18.82,0:19:20.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後就從後門進入工廠的辦公室
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:21.84,0:19:23.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你用最快的速度把石倉先生殺害之後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:24.01,0:19:25.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又把膠帶拆了下來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:26.18,0:19:28.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將現場製造出強盜殺人的樣子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:29.30,0:19:32.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想那個保險箱應該是你早就先弄亂了的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:33.79,0:19:35.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你從辦公室出來的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:36.01,0:19:38.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又再一次打電話給香煙攤的老太太
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:39.64,0:19:40.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:40.67,0:19:43.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就用最快的速度跑到你藏好的另一輛車子那裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:44.00,0:19:45.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把車子開了出來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:45.65,0:19:47.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後到車道轉角去等這幾個孩子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:49.85,0:19:50.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:50.88,0:19:52.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你早就在這輛車子的火星塞上作了手腳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:53.61,0:19:55.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,故意讓它看起來像是引擎出了問題
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:56.07,0:19:58.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連車號也作了一個跟你自己車子相同的號碼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:59.57,0:20:01.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來是這樣呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:01.64,0:20:02.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,實在是太驚人了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:03.60,0:20:04.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你少胡說八道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:04.95,0:20:05.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我撞人逃逸的那輛車子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:06.14,0:20:07.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是被警方沒收的那輛車
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:07.84,0:20:09.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有什麼證據說我不是開那輛車撞人的呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:10.51,0:20:13.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高木刑警 沒收的那輛車子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:14.11,0:20:16.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請問車胎上有沒有壓過泥坑的痕跡呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:17.42,0:20:18.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,泥坑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:18.49,0:20:21.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有 那輛車的輪胎像洗過一樣非常乾淨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:22.07,0:20:24.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是工廠的旁邊明明有一個泥坑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:25.61,0:20:27.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你有開車經過那裡的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:27.60,0:20:30.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那裡的泥巴應該會附在上面才對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:32.38,0:20:33.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們快來查查那輛車的輪胎上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:33.94,0:20:35.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有沒有沾到泥巴的痕跡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:38.07,0:20:39.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的確有 車身下面也一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:40.51,0:20:41.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根本沒有這種事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:42.20,0:20:44.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我車身上的泥巴早就在開車的時候一路磨掉了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:45.67,0:20:46.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偵探先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:47.11,0:20:49.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要是這麼堅持那輛車子就是我撞人逃逸的車子的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:49.62,0:20:51.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就證明給我看看呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:51.66,0:20:52.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒問題
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:53.17,0:20:53.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:55.31,0:20:55.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光彥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:56.64,0:20:58.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用徽章呼叫步美
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:59.19,0:20:59.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用徽章
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:00.37,0:21:02.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是步美的徽章不是已經掉了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:03.41,0:21:04.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你別管了 呼叫看看就是了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:08.45,0:21:09.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,步美 妳聽到我的聲音沒有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:10.69,0:21:13.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽到的話就快點回答 我是光彥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:13.66,0:21:15.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳身上的傷口怎麼樣了呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:15.72,0:21:17.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,待會兒我們就到妳家去看妳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:17.34,0:21:17.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,警部
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:18.33,0:21:19.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這輛車子有這個徽章
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:20.01,0:21:20.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:23.18,0:21:24.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:26.23,0:21:27.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是步美的徽章
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:27.83,0:21:31.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定是被車撞到之後從口袋掉到外面粘到上面的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:31.97,0:21:34.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想利用我們幾個製造不在場的證明
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:35.74,0:21:38.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看樣子反而證明了你自己犯罪的事實哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:42.35,0:21:44.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼可能
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:45.22,0:21:46.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼可能會有這種事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:26.42,0:23:27.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給妳 步美
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:27.69,0:23:28.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳的徽章找到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:31.84,0:23:32.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你 柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:35.47,0:23:36.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:37.34,0:23:38.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎麼可以這樣子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:39.97,0:23:41.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柯南 剛才步美親你哪裡的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:41.49,0:23:43.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們也要親你那個地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:48.59,0:23:49.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說人體模型啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:50.15,0:23:50.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:51.15,0:23:52.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在某個晚上的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:52.44,0:23:54.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在走廊上奔跑啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:55.42,0:23:56.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用很快的速度在跑啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:57.09,0:23:59.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們看 那個玻璃上的白霧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:00.44,0:24:02.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是有人靠著玻璃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:02.52,0:24:03.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,往我們這邊偷看的證據
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:08.34,0:24:08.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是血！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:11.95,0:24:12.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Next Conan
